{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-254-sums-of-digit-factorials","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 254: Jumla za faktoria za tarakimu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tafsiri $f(n)$ kama jumla ya faktoria za tarakimu za $n$. Kwa mfano, $f(342) = 3! + 4! + 2! = 32$.</p>\n<p>Tafsiri $sf(n)$ kama jumla ya tarakimu za $f(n)$. Hivyo $sf(342) = 3 + 2 = 5$.</p>\n<p>Definisati $g(i)$ kao pozitivan ceo broj $n$ takav da $sf(n) = i$. Iako je $sf(342)$ jednako 5, $sf(25)$ takođe je 5, a može se dokazati da je $g(5) = 25$.</p>\n<p>Definišite $sg(i)$ kao zbir cifara od $g(i)$. Dakle, $sg(5) = 2 + 5 = 7$.</p>\n<p>Osim toga, može se dokazati da je $g(20)$ jednako 267 i da je $\\sum sg(i)$ za $1 ≤ i ≤ 20$ jednako 156.</p>\n<p>Koja je vrednost $\\sum sg(i)$ za $1 ≤ i ≤ 150?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f46b1000cf542c50ff7d","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301902,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-254-sums-of-digit-factorials"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sumsOfDigitFactorials() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsumsOfDigitFactorials();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sumsOfDigitFactorials()</code> trebalo bi vratiti <code>8184523820510</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumsOfDigitFactorials(), 8184523820510);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-254-sums-o